_sText: The maximum amount of players is 64, there are 32 spawns on each side. This just makes where the players spawn vary greatly. This map is a smaller, newer, and better version of my last map, GG_abstract_view_b1. The map is more than half the size and half filesize. This map has a custom radar, my first one. The skybox was made specifically for me by my buddy Karatekaefer, thanks mate. I hope you enjoy this map, and I hope to see it on some servers. If you put it on yours, please tell me how the players liked it, thanks everybody. =]
